"""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""""
" Keystrokes - Formatting

" Have Q reformat the current paragraph (or selected text if there is any)
" (default keybinding switches to 'ex' mode):
nnoremap Q gqap
